<plot>A 20-something Brooklyn guy gets out of bed one morning, puts on his slippers and kimono, eats breakfast and sits down at his kitchen window to smoke his morning cigarette. He looks up to a neighboring building's rooftop to find a masked gunman aiming a sniper rifle at him. A gunshot rings out and he wakes up again in bed, thinking it was all a bad dream. . .</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?062901</url></doc>
